    'month' => '01',
    'body' => 'In a message dated 98-01-19 17:28:15 EST, you write:

<< Why does it have to be reactionless? The classic maneuver drive was never
 well defined until SOM - it was just "the drive that moves the ship that
 doesn\'t take fuel".
 
