>
>At 06:32 PM 1/20/98, Ian or Katts wrote:
>>snip<
>>>Bruce,
>>>Some nits to pick 
>>>
>>>1. Bubba carries not only KKM BB\'s but nukes also. 
>>>2. The typical PD will not smudge Bubba\'s paint job, let alone damage
